Lancôme http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lancôme 0 Lancôme (French pronunciation: ​[lɑ̃kom]) is a French luxury perfumes and cosmetics house that distributes products internationally. Lancôme is part of the L'Oréal Luxury Products division, which is its parent company and offers skin care, fragrances, and makeup at higher-end prices.
